 1. Describing a Person (Décrire une personne)
✅ Vocabulary – Physical Appearance:
French	English
grand(e)	tall
petit(e)	short
mince	slim
gros(se)	heavy-set
beau / belle	handsome / beautiful
les cheveux longs	long hair
les cheveux courts	short hair
les yeux bleus / noirs	blue / black eyes

✅ Vocabulary – Personality:
French	English
gentil(le)	kind
drôle	funny
timide	shy
intelligent(e)	smart
sympathique	friendly
méchant(e)	mean

✅ Sentence Patterns:
Il est grand et sportif. → He is tall and athletic.

Elle a les cheveux bruns et les yeux verts. → She has brown hair and green eyes.

C’est une fille intelligente. → She is a smart girl.

✏️ Practice:
Describe a friend using 3 appearance and 2 personality traits.

